// Angular Stater:

1. create new git repo for angular  and clone it to local machine.
2. open terminal and type = 
                ng new ngproject --directory . -g
3. install express
4. create server.js file and write express helloworld program
5. run "ng build" to get dist folder
6. change package.json file add scripts, engines
7. checkpoint save to git
8. deploy to heroku 
9. add link bootstrap.min.js / .min.css / jquery.min.js etc.. tags to index.html file 